Premium Landing Page Redesign
[MODIFY] 
src/pages/LandingPage.jsx
Aesthetics: "Handcrafted" feel, calm color palette, soft gradients. Remove "AI blobs".
Typography: Refine font weights and spacing for a premium look.
Layout: Asymmetrical/staggered layouts for features (breaking the grid).
Animations: Refine GSAP triggers for subtle "slide-away" effects.
Components:
Hero: Minimal, bold headline, scroll cue.
Features: Bento-grid or alternating layout.
Testimonials: Clean, elegant cards.
Footer: Minimalist.
