Settings Pages
Task Management: Create, edit, delete tasks. Verify updates reflect on the board.
Milestones: Add milestones and link tasks. Check progress calculation.
Visualization: Verify Gantt chart renders correctly based on task dates.
Dependencies: specific test to ensure dependent tasks cannot be started/completed if dependencies are unmet (visual warning).
